settings.title: My hands look older than the rest of my body. Which one of your moisturizers can help reverse this curse?
settings.answer: We've got the solution for you: it's a one-two punch of our EXCELLENT MOISTURIZER, followed by a thick slab of SPF 50 MINERAL SUNSCREEN.

settings.title: Do y'all have anything that'll reverse balding?
settings.answer: Sorry friend, we do not. Just embrace it and start using sunscreen on yr dome or maybe wear a cool beanie like all the web developers.

settings.title: Can I get free shipping or what?
settings.answer: Totally, we offer free shipping on all orders over $99.

settings.title: How long does it take to receive international orders?
settings.answer: USPS provides reliable and affordable international delivery to about 180 countries through Priority Mail International. Most Priority Mail International shipments include tracking and insurance.

settings.title: Can I return something if I've used it a lil bit?
settings.answer: How much is a lil bit? Like a lot?

settings.title: What's your window for returns and exchanges?
settings.answer: You have 14 days (from the date of delivery) to return any unopened product for a refund or exchange.
